message.content:
1. U46619-induced fibrinogen binding was unchanged after meal intake with placebo.
2. U46619-induced fibrinogen binding was markedly enhanced after premeal insulin.
3. The enhancement of U46619-induced fibrinogen binding after premeal insulin was by approximately 50-60%.
